Sorry about that.

983
00:36:04,580 --> 00:36:05,460
It's okay.

984
00:36:05,460 --> 00:36:06,920
It's not your fault. It's mine.

985
00:36:06,920 --> 00:36:08,060
Evil meets its retribution.

986
00:36:08,060 --> 00:36:09,100
You can't say it that way.

987
00:36:09,260 --> 00:36:10,400
It's been tough for you, too.

988
00:36:10,980 --> 00:36:12,580
But in the future, if anything happens,

989
00:36:12,580 --> 00:36:13,460
