996
00:36:27,900 --> 00:36:29,220
Let's not mention that anymore.

997
00:36:29,220 --> 00:36:30,180
Water under the bridge.

998
00:36:30,540 --> 00:36:31,420
I asked for you today

999
00:36:31,420 --> 00:36:32,820
